articles.title: Caitlin Clark Makes WNBA History with Double-Double as Fever Lose to Griner, Dream - Bleacher Report
articles.description: Caitlin Clark excelled with 27 points and 11 assists, but the Indiana Fever fell at home to the Atlanta Dream 91-90 on Tuesday.
